            <div class="title">
                Royal Navy (Strength)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1947-10-23/debates/055b9e2c-a426-4b82-b3a7-3974178ecdc2/DebateOnTheAddress" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
